    <div class="row">
        <!-- Image bên trái -->
        <div class="d-none d-md-flex col-md-6 justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <img src="/images/banner_donate_guest.png" alt="Banner" class="floating-image img-fluid" style="width: 80%; object-fit: contain;" />
        </div>

        <!-- Nội dung bên phải -->
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center mt-4 px-4" style="margin-top: 40px;">
            <div style="max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 60px; color: black; font-family: 'Oi', cursive;">COME TO</h1>
                <h1 style="font-size: 90px; color: #bd0026; font-family: 'Oi', cursive;">DONATE</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 20px; color: #333;">
                    From today, with Rosso, thanks to the personalized booking service,
                    you can make an appointment in less than a click at a mobile or fixed collection center.
